== жИКеѓЕгБЃжЬИ ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|и•њжЪ¶}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤}} are {{ill|K≈Н|ja|еЇЪ}} or {{ill|Etsu|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1жЬИ}} is designated as the Bointora {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жЬИ}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Beginning of Spring|ja|зЂЛжШ•}} until the day before {{ill|Awakening of Insects|ja|еХУиЯД}}) as applicable.

== жИКеѓЕгБЃжЧ• ==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йБЄжЧ•|1=Senjitsu}} for Bointora is as follows.
=== Selected Day (йБЄжЧ•) ===
Bointora day is the 1st day of {{ill|Hando|ja|зКѓеЬЯ|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=е∞ПеЬЯ}}.






