It is the 15th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Teiushi|ja|дЄБдЄС|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Kib≈Н|ja|еЈ±еНѓ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Bo|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|еЬЯ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Tiger|ja|еѓЕ|1=Tiger (zodiac)|lt=Tiger (еѓЕ)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|жЬ®|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥#зЫЄеЙЛпЉИгБЭгБЖгБУгБПпЉЙ|lt=Mutual Restraint|lt_ja=зЫЄеЙЛ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (Wood overcomes Earth).

