It is the 15th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Teiushi|ja|дЄБдЄС|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Kib≈Н|ja|еЈ±еНѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Bo|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|еЬЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Tiger|ja|еѓЕ|1=Tiger (zodiac)|lt=Tiger (еѓЕ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|жЬ®|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥#зЫЄеЙЛпЉИгБЭгБЖгБУгБПпЉЙ|lt=Mutual Restraint|lt_ja=зЫЄеЙЛ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) (Wood overcomes Earth).

