== жИКеѓЕгБЃжЬИ ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|и•њжЪ¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=и•њжЪ¶|4=zh|5=еЕђеЕГ|6=es|7=Era com√Їn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|K≈Н|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/K≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Etsu|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|January|ja|1жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January|qq=}} is designated as the Bointora {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Beginning of Spring|ja|зЂЛжШ•|1=Lichun|lt=Risshun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Spring|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Jingzhe|lt=Awakening of Insects|ja|еХУиЯД|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jingzhe|qq=}}) as applicable.

