{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Earth Tiger|kanji=жИКеѓЕ|romaji=tsuchinoe tora|onyomi=boin|p=w√єy√≠n|w=wu-yin|mi=uвБµвБµ  ИЌ° В ∞in¬≤¬є|y=mou6 jan4|j=mou6 jan4|ci=m…Рu j…Рn|mc=m…Щu in|oc-bs=m…Щ  Фin|qq=}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}
'''Yang Earth Tiger also known as жИКеѓЕ''' (tsuchinoetora, bodonotora, boin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 15th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Teiushi|ja|1=Yin Fire Ox|2=ja|дЄБдЄС|1=Yin Fire Ox|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiushi|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Kib≈Н|ja|1=Yin Earth Rabbit|2=ja|еЈ±еНѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kib≈Н|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Bo|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|еЬЯ|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Tiger|ja|еѓЕ|1=Tiger (zodiac)|lt=Tiger (еѓЕ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger|13=User:Immanuelle/Tiger (zodiac)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|жЬ®|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (жЬ®)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood|qq=}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|дЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥#зЫЄеЙЛпЉИгБЭгБЖгБУгБПпЉЙ|lt=Mutual Restraint|lt_ja=зЫЄеЙЛ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Restraint|qq=}}) (Wood overcomes Earth).

