'''Yang Earth Tiger also known as жИКеѓЕ''' (tsuchinoetora, bodonotora, boin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 15th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Teiushi|ja|1=Yin Fire Ox|2=ja|дЄБдЄС|1=Yin Fire Ox|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiushi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Teiushi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Fire Ox|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Kib≈Н|ja|1=Yin Earth Rabbit|2=ja|еЈ±еНѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kib≈Н|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kib≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Earth Rabbit|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°М|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Bo|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|lt=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|2=ja|3=жИК|4=zh|5=жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (еЬЯ)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (еЬЯ)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|2=ru|3=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (—Г-—Б–Є–љ)|4=mn|5=–®–Њ—А–Њ–Њ (–Љ–∞—Е–±–Њ–і)|6=uk|7=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (–£-—Б—Ц–љ)|8=als|9=√Дrde in dr chinesische F√Љmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=ThбїХ (Ng≈© h√†nh)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (еЬЯ)|2=ru|3=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (—Г-—Б–Є–љ)|4=mn|5=–®–Њ—А–Њ–Њ (–Љ–∞—Е–±–Њ–і)|6=uk|7=–Ч–µ–Љ–ї—П (–£-—Б—Ц–љ)|8=als|9=√Дrde in dr chinesische F√Љmf-Elem√§nt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wux