{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Earth Tiger|kanji=жИКеѓЕ|romaji=tsuchinoe tora|onyomi=boin|p=w√єy√≠n|w=wu-yin|mi=uвБµвБµ ИЌ° В ∞in¬≤¬є|y=mou6 jan4|j=mou6 jan4|ci=m…Рu j…Рn|mc=m…Щu in|oc-bs=m…Щ Фin|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yang Earth Tiger also known as жИКеѓЕ''' (tsuchinoetora, bodonotora, boin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|еЕ≠еНБеє≤жФѓ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
