== жИКеѓЕгБЃжЬИ == In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|K≈Н|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|lt=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|2=ja|3=еЇЪ|4=zh|5=еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/K≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/K≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Etsu|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|lt=Kinoto (дєЩ)|2=ja|3=дєЩ|4=zh|5=дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:January|January]] is designated as the Bointora [[:en:Month|Month]]. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]] until the day before [[:en:Jingzhe|Awakening of Insects]]) as applicable.
