--> ==Years of Yang Earth Tiger== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 18 when divided by 60 is a year of Bointora ([[:en:Year|year]]). {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Bointora (жИКеѓЕгБЃеєі)''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 18|18 AD]] * [[:en:AD 78|78 AD]] * [[:en:AD 138|138 AD]] * [[:en:198|198 AD]] * [[:en:258|258 AD]] * [[:en:318|318 AD]] * [[:en:378|378 AD]] * [[:en:438|438 AD]] * [[:en:498|498 AD]] * [[:en:558|558 AD]] * [[:en:618|618 AD]] * [[:en:678|678 AD]] * [[:en:738|738 AD]] * [[:en:798|798 AD]] * [[:en:858|858 AD]] * [[:en:918|918 AD]] * [[:en:978|978 AD]] | * [[:en:1038|1038 AD]] * [[:en:1098|1098 AD]] * [[:en:1158|1158 AD]] * [[:en:1218|1218 AD]] * [[:en:1278|1278 AD]] * [[:en:1338|1338 AD]] * [[:en:1398|1398 AD]] * [[:en:1458|1458 AD]] * [[:en:1518|1518 AD]] * [[:en:1578|1578 AD]] * [[:en:1638|1638 AD]] * [[:en:1698|1698 AD]] * [[:en:1758|1758 AD]] * [[:en:1818|1818 AD]] * [[:en:1878|1878 AD]] * [[:en:1938|1938 AD]] * [[:en:1998|1998 AD]] | * {{ill|2058 AD|ja|2058еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2058|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2058 AD|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} * {{ill|2118 AD|ja|2118еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2118|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2118 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=22дЄЦзіА}} * {{ill|2178 AD|ja|2178еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2178|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2178 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=22дЄЦзіА}} * {{ill|2238 AD|ja|2238еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2238|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2238 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=23дЄЦзіА}} * {{ill|2298 AD|ja|2298еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2298|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2298 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect