ent=changed title based on wikidata|lt=2298 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=23дЄЦзіА|1=23rd century|WD=Q49832}} * {{ill|2358 AD|ja|2358еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2358|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2358 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2418 AD|ja|2418еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2418|comment=changed title based on wikidata|lt=2418 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=25дЄЦзіА|1=25th century|WD=Q49839}} * {{ill|2478 AD|ja|2478еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2478|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2478 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2538 AD|ja|2538еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2538|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2538 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2598 AD|ja|2598еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2598|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2598 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2658 AD|ja|2658еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2658|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2658 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2718 AD|ja|2718еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2718|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2718 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2778 AD|ja|2778еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2778|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2778 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2838 AD|ja|2838еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2838|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2838 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2898 AD|ja|2898еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2898|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2898 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2958 AD|ja|2958еєі|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2958|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2958 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |}
==Months of Yang Earth Tiger== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|K≈Н|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|lt=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|2=ja|3=еЇЪ|4=zh|5=еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/K≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/K≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Etsu|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|lt=Kinoto (дєЩ)|2=ja|3=дєЩ|4=zh|5=дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Etsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:January|January]] is designated as the Bointora [[:en:Month|Month]]. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]] until the day before [[:en:Jingzhe|Awakening of Insects]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yang Earth Tiger== The {{ill|selected day|ja|йБЄжЧ•|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for Bointora is as follows. === Selected Day (йБЄжЧ•) === Bointora day is the 1st day of {{ill|Hando|ja|зКѓеЬЯ|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=е∞ПеЬЯ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hando|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hando|qq=|1=Tsuchi (Japanese term)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11571306}}. ==See Also== *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
